graph TB
    style BROAD fill:#45B7D1,color:#000
    style RED fill:#4ECDC4,color:#000
    style ALLRED fill:#96CEB4,color:#000
    style BAR fill:#FFEAA7,color:#000
    style SG fill:#FF8C42,color:#000

    BROAD[BroadcastShardGroup\nConfig → All Workers\nMPI_Bcast equivalent]
    RED[ReduceShardGroup\nAll Workers → Leader\n7 reduction types: sum/min/max/avg/merge/concat/vote]
    ALLRED[AllReduceShardGroup\nEvery worker gets\naggregated result\nMPI_Allreduce]
    BAR[BarrierShardGroup\nAll workers sync\nbefore next step\nMPI_Barrier]
    SG[ScatterGather\nFan-out work\nFan-in results\nMPI_Scatter + MPI_Gather]
